<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="about-me col-lg-6 col-lg-offset-3">
      <p><h2>Hi im Caitlynn</h2>
        I make cakes in the north fort worth area, if you are interested in having
        me make your next cake you can leave me a message down below.
      </p>
      <div class="container email">
        <form method="POST" action='/'>
          <input type="text" name='email' class="form" placeholder="your-email@email.com" required>
          <button onclick="subscribedmsg()">Subscribe</button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
